def teamFormation():
    n, k = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    a = [int(x) for x in input().split()]
    a.sort()

    if n < k:
        print("NO")
        return

    if k == 1:
        print("YES")
        print(a[0])
        return

    i = 0
    while i < n:
        if i + k > n:
            print("NO")
            return

        if a[i] != a[i+k-1]:
            print("YES")
            print(*[x+1 for x in range(i, i + k)])
            return

        i += k

    print("NO")
    return

teamFormation()

n, k = list(map(int, input().split()))
a = list(map(int, input().split()))

if len(set(a)) < k:
    print("NO")
else:
    print("YES")
    print(*[a.index(i)+1 for i in sorted(set(a))[:k]])
